snippet.title: Kokopa's Atlas - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover new beginnings in Kokopa's Atlas, a curious adventure starring Kokopa and his trusted biodroid companion Pollimero! Explore a new, uncharted world and discover the joys that it holds. Tend your garden, meet quirky friends, catalog all the flora and fauna, or... just relax and enjoy. Grand adventures await, Explorer.

Follow the Dev: https://twitter.com/HyperMegaPixel
Learn more: https://kokopasatlas.com
